Scissors slicing softly, severed strands sigh,  
Sweet Samson's strength slain, swift silenced sky;  
Subtle serpent sheared, sneered secret spite,  
Sacred strands severed, sealing solemn sight;  
Steeled spirit stands steady; strong soul sublime,  
Silent sacrifice soaring, sundered strength sings through time.

